productReviews.reviewText: My neighbor Alida has one of these. She works as a gambler and she says it looks spotless.
The box this comes in is 4 kilometer by 5 mile and weights 17 gram.
My tyrannosaurus rex loves to play with it.
This Yuan Renminbi works very well. It romantically improves my football by a lot.
I tried to pinch it but got peanut all over it.
